        "ggO4iBvuDOP_label": "Submit",
        "ggRuTDi-lX-_text": "<p>As a thank you for joining the Nifora family, enjoy an extra 10% off your next order to try a new mask or restock your favorite. Enter your email below to receive your exclusive discount code and tips from our skincare experts.</p>",
